{"tid":1516081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球安全城市指數：香港急跌至20位","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:39:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c99f428c802580ea83df81e9ab06c862ddab84a2","tid":1516081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"《經濟學人智庫》公布2019年全球安全城市指數，東京、新加坡和大阪蟬聯三甲，香港就由兩年前的第9，急跌至今年的20，四個評分項目有三個急跌，只有「個人安全」一項位列全球第3，而受惡意軟件威脅，令「數碼安全」一項由第5跌至22；而評估應對氣候變化能力，亦令「基建安全」一項跌至18位；「健康安全」排名27。<br />\n<br />\n智庫指出，數據並未考慮最近香港的示威抗議，又指香港依然充滿活力，但如果對基建持續攻擊、政治不穩定性繼續增加、內亂或警民之間關係無法修補，香港分數很可能會下降。<br />\n<br />\n調查對象包括全球60個國家或地區，亞太區城市在頭十位中佔6個，除了東京、新加坡和大阪，還有悉尼、首爾和墨爾本。台北排22，而北京和上海排名31和32，兩個城市所得分數低於總平均分。"},{"pid":"be48c6919ef53f7508faa99a036a2704dfd14494","tid":1516081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1160359&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1160359%26csid%3D261_341&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=3af015da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1160359&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"29eeec2d83a6bd5647fe52a642c357eab7a9100f","tid":1516081,"uid":265179,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"仲有20? 落街隨時被斬, 搭地鐵又會被打, 報警又唔理, 就算係屋企都無端端TG放題, 仲要過期有山埃, CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9cc0c518a359e788764368106255dc82ec6787","tid":1516081,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"毋忘聽日830香港重光紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>830中環見<br />\n830中環見<br />\n830中環見</em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96PXdYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96PXdYs.jpg&h=2d869ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KF8LYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KF8LYC.gif&h=64c0bd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動Post］ 830 感謝勇武暨重光紀念日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2edfa560399affc77f1eedcacf4b1233a67a68a0","tid":1516081,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}